.it 1 an-trap
.nr an-no-space-flag 1
.nr an-break-flag 1
.br
.ps +1
\fBNote\fR
.ps -1
.br
.sp
The reconnection interval may be randomized by 0MQ to prevent reconnection storms in topologies with a large number of peers per socket\&.
.sp .5v
.RE
